  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare two different dosing regimens of phosphatidylcholine
      versus placebo for the induction of remission in ulcerative colitis patients non-responsive
      to standard mesalamine treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
